Ancient Crocodiles

Science Documentary hosted by Nick Shatzki and published by Discovery Channel broadcasted as part of DC Paleoworld series in 1996 - English narration


Information
------------------------------

The 250 million year history of the crocodillians is an evolutionary success story. They have for years been considered the poor relations of the dinosaurs. Discoveries in the Peruvian Amazon and North America have helped palaeontologists to better know and understand them.
